SUMMARY:Live Music Happy Hour Fridays - Eric "T-Bone" Titus - Downtown Santa Rosa
DESCRIPTION:Friday Happy Hour w/ Eric “T-Bone” Titus — live roots-rock & Americana @ Barrel Proof Lounge\, Downtown Santa Rosa. Our comedy show hits at 8\nEvery Friday\, roll into the weekend at Barrel Proof Lounge with Happy Hour sounds from Eric “T-Bone” Titus. This Santa Rosa singer-guitarist blends soulful Americana\, folk-rock\, and classic tunes that pair perfectly with a cold drink and an exhale after the workweek.\nSip $6 beers and enjoy $2 off wine and soju cocktails while T-Bone sets the tone for the night in Downtown Santa Rosa. Then stick around for our signature Friday stand-up comedy show at 8pm\, featuring rotating comics from across the Bay Area and beyond.\nMake Fridays at Barrel Proof Lounge your weekly ritual for live music\, laughs\, and laid-back vibes in Downtown Santa Rosa.\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/live-music-happy-hour-fridays-eric-t-bone-titus-downtown-santa-rosa/2026-03-06/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.44260;-122.71573
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Barrel Proof Lounge 501 Mendocino Avenue Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=501 Mendocino Avenue:geo:-122.71573,38.44260
END:VEVENT
