SUMMARY:Voices that Raised Us: An Evening of Iconic Female Hits from Decades Past (Concert at the Center)
DESCRIPTION:Voices That Raised Us is a heartfelt live music experience celebrating the women whose voices shaped generations. Led by vocalist and acoustic guitarist TJ Carter\, the show journeys through decades of iconic female-driven songs-from the timeless elegance of Patsy Cline to the powerhouse emotion of Adele\, and everything in between. \nWith warmth\, reverence\, and her own soulful interpretation\, TJ brings these beloved songs to life\, honoring the stories\, strength\, and artistry of the women who sang them first-and the listeners who grew up with them. \nBacked by a dynamic four-piece band\, the performance blends intimacy with rich musical depth. The ensemble features: \nJordan Lydon – Percussion\nLyle McKeany – Bass\nDevon Jobson – Electric Guitar \nTogether\, they create a full\, nostalgic\, and emotionally resonant sound that invites audiences to sing along\, reminisce\, and rediscover the music that helped raise us. \nVoices That Raised Us is more than a tribute-it’s a celebration of legacy\, memory\, and the enduring power of women’s voices in music. \nTJ Carter is a singer-songwriter and acoustic guitarist known for her warm\, expressive voice and heartfelt storytelling. Drawing inspiration from folk\, Americana\, and pop influences\, she brings authenticity and emotional depth to every performance. She splits her time between Sonoma\, California and Nashville\, TN. TJ performs both original music and thoughtfully reimagined covers\, connecting audiences to the songs that shaped them-and the stories that continue to resonate today. \nhttps://www.tjcartermusic.com/ \nURLs:\nTickets: https://go.evvnt.com/3459128-0?pid=5514\nWebsite: https://go.evvnt.com/3459128-2?pid=5514 \nDate and Time: On Fri\, 06 Mar 2026 19:00 – 21:00 \nVenue details: Sonoma Community Center\, 276 East Napa Street\, Sonoma\, California\, 95476\, United States \nCategory: Live Music \nPrice: General Admission: USD 25.00
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/voices-that-raised-us-an-evening-of-iconic-female-hits-from-decades-past-concert-at-the-center/
LOCATION:Sonoma Community Center\, 276 East Napa Street\, Sonoma\, 95476
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.2918;-122.453
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Sonoma Community Center 276 East Napa Street Sonoma 95476;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=276 East Napa Street:geo:-122.453,38.2918
END:VEVENT
