SUMMARY:Comedy Queens
DESCRIPTION:Laugh along with some of the bay area’s funniest comedians who spin the headlines of their lives into memorable punchlines. Real Life\, Real Funny.\nYou’ve seen these ladies at the San Francisco Comedy Competition\, Burbank Comedy Festival\, Throckmorton Theatre\, on commercials (Ancestry.com)\, Rooster T Feathers\, SketchFest\, Cobb’s\, The Punch Line SF\, Alameda Comedy Club\, The Improv and more. Join us for a hilarious night of comedy! Comedians: Kathy Guest\, Sue Alfieri\, and Rhoda Gravador. AND special guest…. \nBUY TICKETS IN ADVANCE AND SAVE!\nTickets $25 in advance. Tickets at the door $30.\nDOORS OPEN AT 6:30 PM.\nADULT MATERIAL. 18+
