SUMMARY:Neon Night – 70s to Now Dance Party
DESCRIPTION:Neon Night – 70s to Now Dance Party\nFeaturing DJ Sleepless\nBarrel Proof Lounge | Downtown Santa Rosa\nWhen the comedy ends\, the lights shift.\nAt 10PM\, DJ Sleepless takes control for Neon Night — a high-energy dance party spanning decades of pure movement. From the bass lines of ABBA to the guitar fire of Prince\, with a little Britney sparkle in between\, this is wall-to-wall dance floor fuel from the 70s to now.\nDJ Sleepless keeps the pulse steady and the floor moving — blending disco grooves\, 80s synth\, 90s pop chaos\, and modern dance anthems into one seamless\, sweat-ready night.\nThis isn’t background music.\nIt’s a dance floor.\nNo cover.\nNo standing around.\nNo backs on the wall.\nBeer\, wine & Soju cocktails flowing\nComedy at 8PM\nNeon Night with DJ Sleepless at 10PM\nFREE entry\n501 Mendocino Avenue\, Downtown Santa Rosa.\nCome for the laughs. Stay for the sweat.\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/neon-night-70s-to-now-dance-party/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music,Other
